    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a premier balance of performance and long-term reliability. This unit has undergone a thorough professional assessment to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal remain at a high standard. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, this vehicle represents a sophisticated choice for those who demand quality and consistency in their daily commute. A comprehensive service history is available upon request.",
      "price": 34850.0,
